OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778490376
OL,3,CFundraiser for teen footballers
OL,4,Cinjured in e-bike crash
OL,6,FThe organisers of a fundraiser for two
OL,7,Fteenage footballers, seriously injured
OL,8,Fin an e-bike crash, say they've been
OL,9,F'blown away' by the public's response.
OL,11,FNicole, 15, and Lexi, 14, who play for
OL,12,FFarnborough FC's U15 Girls, suffered
OL,13,Fhead injuries and multiple fractures
OL,14,Fwhen the bike they were riding
OL,15,Fcollided with a car in their home town
OL,16,Fon Friday 1 May.
OL,18,FThey were rushed to hospital in London
OL,19,F, where both girls have undergone
OL,20,Foperations and are responding well.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
