FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778490376
OL,3,CFundraiser for teen footballers
OL,4,Cinjured in e-bike crash
OL,6,FBut their recovery is expected to take
OL,7,Fmany months, and team coach, Mike
OL,8,FJones, set up a fundraiser to help
OL,9,Ffund specialist physiotherapy and
OL,10,Fequipment, to get them back on the
OL,11,Fpitch.
OL,13,FIn just over a week they've smashed
OL,14,Ftheir target, raising almost #7000.
OL,16,FPosting on the Go Fund Me website,
OL,17,FMike said the girls and their families
OL,18,Fhad the support of everyone at the club
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778490376
OL,3,CFundraiser for teen footballers
OL,4,Cinjured in e-bike crash
OL,6,FHe wrote: "Although the team has just
OL,7,Fsecured the Division 2 league title at
OL,8,FU15s, we are holding off on all
OL,9,Fcelebrations.
OL,11,F"We have made the collective decision
OL,12,Fthat we cannot and will not celebrate
OL,13,Fthe girls success until Coley and Lex
OL,14,Fare back with us to share it.
OL,16,F"A league title win means nothing to
OL,17,Fus without every single girl who
OL,18,Fplayed their part being there."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
